  "time_ut": 1657791651,
  "original_lang": "si",
  "original_title": "\u0dc4\u0db8\u0dd4\u0daf\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0daf\u0dd0\u0da9\u0dd2 \u0db1\u0dd2\u0dc0\u0dda\u0daf\u0db1\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A strong announcement from the army",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "In a statement, the army informs that the responsibility of protecting the public property as well as all the places and public lives has been assigned to the army, and that the army will not hesitate to use that power at all.",
        "The army informs that the perpetrators themselves should bear the responsibility for the consequences that may arise in such a situation.",
        "The Chief of Defense Staff, Triwida Army Commanders and the Inspector General of Police strongly requested the protestors to be peaceful on more than three occasions, to protect the state buildings and all properties and to resolve the situation arising with the departure of President Gotabhaya Rajapaksa in accordance with the constitution.",
        "All those who are increasing violence in order to damage the security forces or public property should immediately refrain from such acts of violence or else the security forces will have to use all the powers in accordance with the existing conditions and in the future they will be assigned the corresponding responsibility to protect public property as well as all places and public lives. It is further emphasized that the security forces are not at all reluctant to use that force and the responsibility for the consequences that may arise in such a situation should be borne by these violent people themselves."
      ],
